snippet.title: Banjo Pilot (GBA) Longplay [312]
snippet.description: Played for the first time, this is a pretty decent mario kart clone with banjo kazooie characters for GBA. I'm terribad at games like this but it shows that this game is pretty simple if I can beat it with not much issues. Good music and sprites and kind of fun, but a little bare bones.
